  AURUM PROTOCOL - SYSTEM WORKFLOW & ARCHITECTURE
  Autonomous AI Credit Bureau on Casper Network
================================================================================

================================================================================
  WHAT IS AURUM?
================================================================================

  You submit a Casper wallet address.
  Six AI agents analyze it.
  A credit score (0-1000) is minted on-chain via Casper contracts.
  Third parties pay CSPR to query that score via an x402 micropayment gate.

  No usernames. No banks. Just on-chain behavior.

  Deployment status (June 2026):
    - 4 smart contracts live on casper-test
    - API runs locally (localhost:8000), not yet publicly hosted
    - Supabase + Groq are cloud services (not on Casper)


