                       live  ->  signs and submits deploys via casper-client
                                 put-deploy --session-hash (Odra v1 contracts)
                               [currently: live]

  X402_MODE            mock  ->  proof accepted on structure alone
                       live  ->  structure check + on-chain transfer scan
