    deploy_mode, cspr_cloud_mode, network, contracts { credit_registry,
    compliance_registry, oracle_paywall, reputation_registry }


================================================================================
  SCORING MODEL
================================================================================

  XGBoost trained on 6 features, each 0-100:

  Feature            Source                           Weight (approx)
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------
  repayment          loan repayment ratio             highest
  wallet_activity    tx count + counterparty spread   high
  income             inbound / total CSPR flow        high
  defi               active liquidity positions       medium
  rwa                real-world asset events          medium
  dao                yield events (governance proxy)  lower

  Output:  raw score  ->  scaled to 0-1000
  SHAP explains which features drove the score up or down.


